data.description: Welcome home. This adorable  Bi-level features 4 bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms.  On the lower level you’ll find  a spacious living room with access to a fenced in yard and a half bath.   Dining room, kitchen, and full bathroom are on the upper level.  An open floor plan makes this perfect the perfect place to host all of your family parties. Kitchen features granite Counter tops, tile backsplash and flawless white cabinets.  Down the hall you will find 3 spacious bedrooms.   Both bathrooms feature newer vanities with granite tops, and neutral tile flooring.  Outside features a new shed for storage and lots of space for grilling and relaxing. This very well maintained property is waiting for you, and will not last long. Schedule your tour today!
